
# Boys & Girls Club Donor Analysis

## Project Overview

The Boys & Girls Club (BGC) maintains donor data across multiple sources, including spreadsheets and manual records. This fragmentation makes it difficult to gain a clear understanding of donor behavior, track fundraising performance, and support data-driven decision-making.

## Objective

The goal of this project is to explore donor data and identify patterns in donation behavior that can help improve fundraising strategies and donor engagement.

## Approach

To achieve this, I:
- Loaded and reviewed the dataset
- Cleaned and standardized the data
- Performed exploratory data analysis (EDA)
- Created visualizations to highlight key trends

## Note

All data used in this project has been anonymized and aggregated to protect privacy.

**Note:** The original dataset is not included in this repository to protect privacy.




